{
  "page": "The Reckoning of Time",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>The Reckoning of Time</b></i> was written by Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Walgram\" title=\"Walgram\">Walgram</a>. It is considered to be a great work, which delves deeply into the problem of studying ancient records when various cultures reckon <a href=\"/index.php/Measurement#Units_of_time_measurement\" title=\"Measurement\">days, seasons, and years</a> differently.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafother_lands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafother_lands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Reckoning_of_Time&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafother_lands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafother_lands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Other Lands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403125350\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.028 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.313 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 101/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8555/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 327/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 73/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion dep